Document: BoxMesh
Path: godot/classes/class_boxmesh.rst
Summary: Properties and their descriptions for the BoxMesh class, including size and subdivision parameters.

Vector3 size = Vector3(1, 1, 1). Set/Get: set_size(value: Vector3), get_size() → Vector3. The box's width, height and depth.

Integer subdivide_depth = 0. Set/Get: set_subdivide_depth(value: int), get_subdivide_depth() → int. Number of extra edge loops inserted along the Z axis.

Integer subdivide_height = 0. Set/Get: set_subdivide_height(value: int), get_subdivide_height() → int. Number of extra edge loops inserted along the Y axis.

Integer subdivide_width = 0. Set/Get: set_subdivide_width(value: int), get_subdivide_width() → int. Number of extra edge loops inserted along the X axis.